{"tid":2460254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛回家Bonnie林凱恩阿哥唔出糧比裝修工人加工程爛尾？","createTime":"2021-03-24T17:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T08:28:53.000Z","uid":84308,"like":195,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"36068696509bc277b47fbbe52ed8b0501759dd35","tid":2460254,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"尋人啟事再黎過<br />\n林祥晉 <br />\n職業：裝修判頭<br />\nTVB藝員 愛回家 林凱恩 親生呀哥<br />\n現負責兩個住家裝修<br />\n1. 北角富雅花園金桃閣14樓某室 （爛尾）<br />\n2.沙田圍博康邨博達樓16樓某室 （爛尾）<br />\n於2021年3月19號失去聯絡<br />\n兩個業主已報警 <br />\n現欠裝修工人 人工同兩個裝修工程爛尾<br />\n林凱恩 Iris Lam 林小姐 你呀哥失蹤兩三日 我尋日po完一個鐘都冇 你呀哥就托人搵我叫我del po 一日 我即刻del 我讓左步 但係你呀哥都仲係唔浦頭wow<br />\n電話都冇個 你不如報下警啦 我好擔心你呀哥有咩事呀 搞到人地間屋爛尾 仲拖欠薪金 <br />\n<br />\n（ps 林祥晉尋晚凌晨曾經wts 上過線 ）<br />\n東張西望<br />\n01娛樂<br />\nTVB<br />\nmyTV SUPER<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbWNVTBjzMwoSHfMwByx3W95tdhYQriTcFgGtwFsVPgTw?filename=mVwhn5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVwhn5R.jpg&h=c1b8f9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPcRaRkeLdVjryJv8ojwHYCQXEGh9GqhAD9qqwEiD3XzH?filename=iNeZBqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNeZBqR.jpg&h=702a33a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd6XDKFcDYx5EGA1ySRuDSE4nJaaigytJDtmqLb2Grh7L?filename=SJMk5jc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJMk5jc.jpg&h=4dccef6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/03/25/010854_0d81ebad97b2f0d3bf02decb126e4943.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F03%2F25%2F010854_0d81ebad97b2f0d3bf02decb126e4943.jpeg&h=b4ff6e05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/03/25/010856_0bc9e1d331b95fe6d4befa1adc870661.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F03%2F25%2F010856